Manuel Pellegrini has been named the Premier League Manager of the Month for December after the Chilean guided Manchester City to five wins last month.

The Premier League champions were unbeaten in the month of December and claimed 16 points from a possible 18 in the league.

It was a run of form that helped City claw back eight-point deficit on league-leaders Chelsea to end 2014 within touching distance of the top of the table.

