Edin Dzeko and Steven Jovetic also spent much of the month injured but City still managed to score 14 goals in just six Premier League matches matches.

It is the third time Pellegrini has won the award during his 18-month spell in the Premier League, winning it for consecutive months in December 2013 and January 2014.

QPR striker Charlie Austin won the player of the month for December.

 

